des: Coffee is one of the most widely consumed beverages around the world and is a central and popular part of our culture. An estimated 3.5 billion cups of coffee are consumed worldwide every day. Pulled from throughout the ages, from writers to actors, here are great coffee quotes that will pair perfectly with your morning cup. Simply ask Alexa: "Alexa Open coffee quotes".
